#: ../../migration.rst:2
msgid "Migration Guide"
msgstr "迁移指南"

#: ../../migration.rst:4
msgid "This guide helps you upgrade from older versions of CodeVideoRenderer."
msgstr "本指南帮助您从旧版本升级 CodeVideoRenderer。"

#: ../../migration.rst:7
msgid "Migrating to 1.2.x"
msgstr "迁移到 1.2.x"

#: ../../migration.rst:9
msgid ""
"Version 1.2.x introduced breaking API changes. Follow the sections below "
"when upgrading from 1.1.x or earlier."
msgstr "1.2.x 版本引入了破坏性的 API 更改。从 1.1.x 或更早版本升级时，请遵循以下部分。"

#: ../../migration.rst:12
msgid "Function Naming Convention"
msgstr "函数命名规范"

#: ../../migration.rst:14
msgid ""
"All public functions and classes switched from **snake_case** to "
"**camelCase** in 1.2.1."
msgstr "1.2.1 版本中，所有公共函数和类都从 **snake_case** 切换为 **camelCase**。"

#: ../../migration.rst:20
msgid "Old (1.1.x and earlier)"
msgstr "旧版（1.1.x 及更早）"

#: ../../migration.rst:21
msgid "New (1.2.x)"
msgstr "新版（1.2.x）"

#: ../../migration.rst:22
msgid "``type_checker``"
msgstr "``type_checker``"

#: ../../migration.rst:23 ../../migration.rst:33
msgid "``typeChecker``"
msgstr "``typeChecker``"

#: ../../migration.rst:25
msgid ""
"If you were calling utility functions directly from "
"``CodeVideoRenderer.utils``, update your code accordingly."
msgstr "如果您直接从 ``CodeVideoRenderer.utils`` 调用实用函数，请相应地更新代码。"

#: ../../migration.rst:28
msgid "Removed Utilities"
msgstr "已移除的实用函数"

#: ../../migration.rst:30
msgid "The following functions were removed from ``utils.py`` in 1.2.3:"
msgstr "以下函数在 1.2.3 版本中被从 ``utils.py`` 中移除："

#: ../../migration.rst:32
msgid "``checkType``"
msgstr "``checkType``"

#: ../../migration.rst:35
msgid ""
"If your own code depends on these functions, replace them with "
"``typeguard.typechecked`` (which CodeVideoRenderer now uses internally) or "
"implement your own type checking."
msgstr ""
"如果您自己的代码依赖于这些函数，请将其替换为 ``typeguard.typechecked``\\ （CodeVideoRenderer "
"现在内部使用）或实现自己的类型检查。"

#: ../../migration.rst:38
msgid "No Action Needed for Basic Usage"
msgstr "基本用法无需操作"

#: ../../migration.rst:40
msgid ""
"If you only use the high-level :class:`~.CameraFollowCursorCV` API (as shown"
" in :doc:`tutorials`), no code changes are required—the breaking changes "
"affect internal utilities and direct imports from ``utils.py``."
msgstr ""
"如果您仅使用高级 :class:`~.CameraFollowCursorCV` API（如 :doc:`tutorials` "
"中所示），则无需更改代码—破坏性更改仅影响内部实用函数和直接从 ``utils.py`` 导入的内容。"
